data.description: Discover an unparalleled lifestyle and investment opportunity in Roseburg's historic Mill/Pine District! Presenting a rare, two-home property offering the best of both worlds. Live in the lovingly refurbished 953 sq ft, 2-bedroom, 1-bath main house, featuring a gourmet kitchen with brand new Cherry Wood cabinets and extensive remodeling. Enjoy the warm comfort of new carpets in the bedrooms and living room, efficient gas heating, and a generous laundry room for seamless living. Adjacent to this charming home is a 576 sq ft, 1-bedroom, 1-bath second unit, currently rented for $1,050 per month. This turnkey rental property comes complete with fresh paint, a newer roof, and lots of remodeling, offering you the flexibility to generate steady income through Airbnb bookings or as a long-term rental. The unit also boasts convenient alley access and off-alley parking, making it a desirable choice for tenants or guests. Tourists will love the chance to opt for this historic charmer! Both homes feature newer roofs, updated flooring, fresh interior and exterior paint, and upgraded bathrooms. Located close to town in a convenient setting, you're just minutes away from restaurants, shopping, and scenic spots. This versatile property will qualify for various loan programs, making it an exceptional choice for a wide range of investors and homeowners. Don't miss this once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to elevate your lifestyle while also securing a smart investment. Schedule your private tour today!
